title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 16
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Dave is upset with Rico for not delivering his holiday gift in time for Hanukkah. Big Cat is coming off a huge week and remains in the lead for the Pat Hill trophy heading into Championship Weekend!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
